  On a $\varphi(1) = 1$. Soit $(P,Q) \in (Q[X])^{2}$.
  $$
    \varphi(P+Q) = \tilde{P+Q}(\sqrt{2}) = \tilde{P}(\sqrt{2}) + \tilde{Q}(\sqrt{2}) = \varphi(P) + \varphi(Q)
